                <h1>Former Pentagon official talks Obama foreign policy</h1>
                
                                    <figure class="dom-art-container my-4">
                                                    <img src="https://snworksceo.imgix.net/dtc/cd811121-1539-4fc8-a498-b761b14773d0.sized-1000x1000.jpg?w=1000" alt="The&#x20;Devils&#x20;took&#x20;down&#x20;the&#x20;Florida&#x20;State&#x20;Seminoles,&#x20;previously&#x20;undefeated&#x20;in&#x20;the&#x20;ACC,&#x20;Saturday&#x20;at&#x20;Indoor&#x20;Cameron&#x20;Stadium" class="w-100">
                                                <div class="domphoto-caption mt-2 text-left text-md-right">
                            The Devils took down the Florida State Seminoles, previously undefeated in the ACC, Saturday at Indoor Cameron Stadium

                                                             <aside class="photo-caption photo-credit d-block pl-1">
                                    <figcaption class="d-block">
